&lt;p&gt;The DH Pace Company is a family-owned and privately held business with annual sales over $1 billion through 60+ offices located across the continental United States. The Company is an industry leader in the distribution, installation, maintenance, and repair of a complete range of commercial, industrial, and residential door, docking and security products. In 2026, DH Pace is celebrating its 100&lt;sup&gt;th&lt;/sup&gt; anniversary in business.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;p&gt;DH Pace Company, Inc. is seeking an &lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(224, 62, 45);&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Account Coordinator&lt;/strong&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;to join our Nationwide Service Team in Olathe, KS. An Account Coordinator is the liaison between internal technicians, vendors, and subcontractors, and the nation-wide clients that we serve. You will be responsible for client communication, problem-solving, and basic account management.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
