&lt;p&gt;The DH Pace Company is a family-owned and privately held business with annual sales over $1 billion through 60+ offices located across the continental United States. The Company is an industry leader in the distribution, installation, maintenance, and repair of a complete range of commercial, industrial, and residential door, docking and security products. In 2026, DH Pace is celebrating its 100&lt;sup&gt;th&lt;/sup&gt; anniversary in business.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;DH Pace Company, Inc.&lt;/strong&gt;, is seeking experienced &lt;strong&gt;Automatic Door Technicians/Installers&lt;/strong&gt; in the &lt;strong&gt;Northern&amp;nbsp;Mississippi area&lt;/strong&gt;. You will be working on a variety of automatic door systems, including revolving, sliding, folding, and swinging doors. If you have a mechanical and electrical aptitude and have experience with access control, hollow metal, or auto doors, please apply!&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Job Responsibilities:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Install and/or repair a wide range of automatic doors and door hardware, including swinging, sliding, bi-folding and revolving doors&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Identify opportunities to provide customers with products and services&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Track and maintain job related paperwork and submit in a timely manner&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Operate in safety conscious manner at all times while performing job duties&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Other duties as assigned&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Job Qualifications:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;High School Diploma/GED preferred&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Prior experience in a similar role or one that required a mechanical and electrical aptitude preferred&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Ability to safely lift up to 100 pounds&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Ability to work at heights and use a ladder&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Must possess valid driver’s license and good driving record&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;AAADM Certification Preferred&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;content-conclusion&quot;&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;What We Offer&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Comprehensive medical, dental, and vision coverage — available your first full month&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Generous paid time off plus paid holidays and floating holidays&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Company-paid life insurance, short-term disability, and long-term disability&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;401(k) with employer match&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Health Savings Account (HSA) and Flexible Spending Account (FSA) options&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Voluntary benefits including supplemental life and critical illness coverage&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Employee discounts for you and your immediate family&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Competitive compensation with annual performance reviews&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
